  <summary date="2021-04-15T14:27:26Z" status="Introduced in House">American Innovation and R&amp;D Competitiveness Act of 2021

This bill eliminates the five-year amortization requirement for research and experimental expenditures scheduled to begin in 2022, thus allowing continued expensing of such expenditures in the taxable years in which they are incurred.</summary>
